{"tid":1624118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔敢上前線嘅，唔該做呢樣嘢","createTime":"2019-10-05T02:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:58:11.000Z","uid":53000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54dc76567665f54bd73294cf2867a66b24b5ce57","tid":1624118,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:58:11.000Z","msg":"（外媒心水清！）對於琴晚好多商店被打破，BBC客觀描述示威者是攻擊「親北京」嘅舖頭，完全沒有被689誤導(CY和一班政府官員不斷抹黑示威者是恐怖分子，￼無差別襲擊商店和途人，企圖打國際輿論戰）￼￼<br />\n<br />\n另外從標題和內文，BBC都明示暗示出，示威者武力升級是因為政府（強推禁蒙面法和警察開實彈）！而琴晚香港出現的係群眾自發的Unplanned Protests！文中更提及10月1日一名警官射擊的是示威者（Demonstrator）而唔係暴徒！另外亦提到一名14歲人士係琴晚被射傷腳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，狠人再次鼓勵咁多位唔能夠上前線的和理非們，打好國際輿論戰是我地最能支持前線手足的方法，港共政府一定會繼續出唔同嘅奸招去抹黑示威者￼，我地要全力應付，唔好怠慢和輕敵！￼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49939173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49939173&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqvch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=c30a73b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49939173&h=21e69c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49939173</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KB7CGnq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKB7CGnq.jpg&h=21c82ba0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}